      // ── Brew: virtual router model for the Brew application ─────────────────
      // Routes traffic to the optimal Hermes profile based on task classification:
      //   Code/development questions  → derp-lead or derp-coder
      //   Architecture/design         → derp-thinker
      //   Infrastructure/Proxmox/OPNsense → derp-server (via General fallback)
      //   General conversation        → default (derp dispatcher)
      // Hermes profiles are tried first, then cloud fallbacks if unavailable.
